Route 53
    :Configure and Manager web domains for websites or applications you host on AWS.

    - Domain Registration: 
        :such as exemple.com

    - DNS (Domain Name System) Service:
        :exemple.com > 192.0.2.1

    - Health Checking:
        :verify that it's Reachable, Available and Functional

    - Pricing:
        : Free Tier is not available

    - Configure:
        1- Number of hosted zones
        2- Traffica flow (per policy)
        3- Standard queries
        4- Latency based routing
        5- Geo DNS queries
        6- Health checks
        7- Register/Transfer a domain


https://docs.aws.amazon.com/Route53/latest/DeveloperGuide/Welcome.html
